entries.title: John Deere allows Illinois farmers to repair their own equipment
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Ending a standoff that has lasted for years, Illinois farmers now have the right to repair their John Deere tractors themselves.

entries.title: Abortion protection bill passes both Illinois chambers
entries.description: (The Center Square) – After heated debate from state lawmakers throughout the lame-duck session, a measure that aims to increase access to abortion and gender reassignment procedures in Illinois has passed both chambers.

entries.title: Republicans blast Biden over classified documents, raise questions of double standard
entries.description: (The Center Square) – President Joe Biden has come under heavy fire after news reports indicated that classified documents from his time as vice president were found at the Penn Biden Center for Diplomacy and Global Engagement in Washington.
